---

<footer class="py-20 bg-[#2D2D2D] text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-20 mb-20">
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-bold font-display inline-block mb-8 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
          M.<span class="text-white/60">Menuiserie</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-white/40 max-w-sm leading-relaxed mb-10 italic-serif text-2xl font-normal">
          "Menuisier de père en fils, nous perpétuons la tradition du bois avec modernité et exigence au cœur de la Province de Liège."
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="#" class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-white/50 hover:text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-white/50 hover:text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest text-[#5D4037]">Navigation</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-white/60 font-medium">
          <li><a href="#accueil" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Accueil</a></li>
          <li><a href="#services" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Mes Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="#portfolio" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Nos Projets</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Devis & Tarifs</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest text-[#5D4037]">Zone d'intervention</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
          <li>Liège (Centre, Coronmeuse, Grivegnée)</li>
          <li>Chaudfontaine, Embourg</li>
          <li>Neupré, Boncelles</li>
          <li>Herstal, Oupeye</li>
          <li>Verviers, Spa</li>
          <li>Et toute la Province de Liège</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 opacity-40 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} M.Menuiserie - Liège, Belgique</p>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Mentions Légales</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Politique de confidentialité</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
